{"tid":371880,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[母親的決擇] 外置HDD選擇 LACIE D2 V.S G-TECH DRIVE","createTime":"2017-08-24T03:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T08:40:33.000Z","uid":119986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb83c5e983ffcfb2e19d3d48ec84775ec7e0dbc","tid":371880,"uid":119986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"電腦：MACBOOK PRO 17年<br />\n系統：MAC OS ＋ BOOT CAMP WINDOW 10<br />\n企圖：<span style=\"color: red;\">長開</span>剪片/畫圖用 3D ，AI， PS 用，BACK UP FILE<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耐用度，兼容性？，可長插同埋直接係隻HDD工作？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. LaCie 4TB d2 Thunderbolt 2 &amp; USB 3.0 硬碟   <span style=\"color: red;\">HK$2,698</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另須買 雷電2 轉雷電3轉插 HK$388.00</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HFY82PA/B/lacie-4tb-d2-thunderbolt-2-usb-30-%E7%A1%AC%E7%A2%9F?afid=p238%7CsKgsYLZ4d-dc_mtid_18707vxu38484_pcrid_178766336090_&amp;cid=aos-hk-kwgo-pla-btb-product-HFY82PA/B-HKZH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk-zh%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FHFY82PA%2FB%2Flacie-4tb-d2-thunderbolt-2-usb-30-%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E7%25A2%259F%3Fafid%3Dp238%257CsKgsYLZ4d-dc_mtid_18707vxu38484_pcrid_178766336090_%26cid%3Daos-hk-kwgo-pla-btb-product-HFY82PA%2FB-HKZH&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79adtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0f3a9336\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HFY82PA/B/lacie-4tb-d2-thunderbolt-2-usb-30-%E7%A1%AC%E7%A2%9F?afid=p238%7CsKgsYLZ4d-dc_mtid_18707vxu38484_pcrid_178766336090_&amp;cid=aos-hk-kwgo-pla-btb-product-HFY82PA/B-HKZH</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/110336_b241a937de5b6776cf2a058da18e58eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F110336_b241a937de5b6776cf2a058da18e58eb.jpg&h=61436c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. G-Technology 4TB G-DRIVE Thunderbolt 3 外置硬碟  <span style=\"color: red;\">HK$3,148</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HLAB2ZM/A/g-technology-4tb-g-drive-thunderbolt-3-%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%AE%E7%A1%AC%E7%A2%9F?fnode=5f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk-zh%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FHLAB2ZM%2FA%2Fg-technology-4tb-g-drive-thunderbolt-3-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E7%25A2%259F%3Ffnode%3D5f&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79adtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c0aff1c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HLAB2ZM/A/g-technology-4tb-g-drive-thunderbolt-3-%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%AE%E7%A1%AC%E7%A2%9F?fnode=5f</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/110525_77f4fe2217b3aa9f21b5cee49cd4af2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F110525_77f4fe2217b3aa9f21b5cee49cd4af2f.jpg&h=19ec89bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMANY THANKS"},{"pid":"8c4e23ff681f790934e3c15e5716d21b34f9be19","tid":371880,"uid":119986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"因為牌子評價好似LACIE 好D 所以想乞下意見"},{"pid":"61429fe0a5016204e86697e50b39d68335c735d1","tid":371880,"uid":119986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75932cd6d4c87cbbfdbe9c84931cc11c8f3821c1","tid":371880,"uid":119986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ec38081a741ad3ab09c22c9703e4d42cee2ba","tid":371880,"uid":119986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235ec259cc9a303e15668c0fcba1559426fed6ca","tid":371880,"uid":1199