ld computering出果d<br />\n再keep住買hgst d hdd黎用<br />\n咁會化算過你連housing買lacie或者g-tech嘅單harddisk版<br />\n<br />\n依度都夠我用一個星期左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/013258_cadd62f1c144081f4e6456d13828e63e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F013258_cadd62f1c144081f4e6456d13828e63e.jpg&h=08301842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解果陣買lacie唔買g-raid係因為代理話我要咁多等下個船期先有，我又急住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eebf00dc2aeeed8bdf0f70cbeba9b99149c066","tid":371880,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申： 工作需要，我每日都要消耗4TB左右，如果你唔係需要hardware raid，大可以買隻thunderbolt 嘅hdd dock e.g. akitio或者other world computering出果d<br />\n再keep住買hgst d hdd黎用<br />\n咁會化算過你連housing買lacie或者g-tech嘅單harddisk版<br />\n<br />\n依度都夠我用一個星期左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/013258_cadd62f1c144081f4e6456d13828e63e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F013258_cadd62f1c144081f4e6456d13828e63e.jpg&h=08301842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解果陣買lacie唔買g-raid係因為代理話我要咁多等下個船期先有，我又急住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWow 大哥你點做管理？"},{"pid":"f4db2b967658d89754b66532800d671c400ccc6b","tid":371880,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申： 工作需要，我每日都要消耗4TB左右，如果你唔係需要hardware raid，大可以買隻thunderbolt 嘅hdd dock e.g. akitio或者other world computering出果d<br />\n再keep住買hgst d hdd黎用<br />\n咁會化算過你連housing買lacie或者g-tech嘅單harddisk版<br />\n<br />\n依度都夠我用一個星期左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/013258_cadd62f1c144081f4e6456d13828e63e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F013258_cadd62f1c144081f4e6456d13828e63e.jpg&h=08301842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解果陣買lacie唔買g-raid係因為代理話我要咁多等下個船期先有，我又急住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAV 達人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f27f1e8ee7cb2e5cee8a2c3a5b9ec2c95b14f5d","tid":371880,"uid":17404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/210032_ac729adb11642991a79e8c1c40805afe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F210032_ac729adb11642991a79e8c1c40805afe.jpg&h=4f2eb5ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對seagate真係冇乜好感<br />\n<br />\n其實上網好多類似圖表比較，唔同scenario  有唔同結果，有時journalist想煮死一個brand好易。我盡量找差不多條件去比較<br />\n<br />\n利申以前用過seagate真係死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739259163db1185a369e9f65d40b8405895dc336","tid":371880,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"My book"},{"pid":"5c3ed1b24ae961841184e6c6cf906178b2b5863d","tid":371880,"uid":17404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"其實thunderbolt技術對比hdd實在太先進。hdd轉數行tb 只係用到tb速度好小部分。速度嘅Bottleneck喺hdd果度，所以而家行單碟用tb我唔知有冇需要，如果考慮價錢貴一大截嘅因素<br />\n<br />\n如果好有米用TB + ssd 會合理D。<br />\n<br />\n如果要大儲存空間 應該行raid - tb 未必係改善速度嘅因素，但係買穩定同將來compatibility"},{"pid":"4229132144899b844d3302c525675cf5a9e2f785","tid":371880,"uid":68446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T20:20:05.000Z","msg":"首先上面都講左，盡搵包WD或者HGST既牌子，或者自己砌<br />\n<br />\n單HDD無咩理由唔用USB-A 3.0 / USB-C 3.1，只係百幾二百MB/s<br />\n就算孖碟RAID0都係去到400-500MB/s呢度用USB都夠<br />\n不過行TB3做頭係可以確保daisy chain以後既device夠bandwidth，變相唔會浪費你個TB3 port<br />\n我用iMac 2017得兩個TB3，就係呢個原因(啱啱)買左G-Tech隻G-RAID 16TB<br />\n我唔需要個TB port俾電，不過想要個drive有多一個TB3 pass through，同埋bonus係佢有多一個HDMI 2.0出mon<br />\n<br />\nbtw你揀嗰兩隻性價比幾差，衣家一個8TB既WD NAS Red或者HGST NAS都係兩千，想要7200rpm既server HDD都係三千內<br />\n你可以用WD My Book系列做參考，究竟一隻外置碟個interface應該值幾多<br />\n你嗰兩隻因為TB1/2而值過千不過只係單碟有d浪費<br />\n其實四千鬆已經買到G-RAID Thunderbolt 3 4+4TB"},{"pid":"25e6c2c0111266ea9ba23a1b54ddfa427a4c85bc","tid":371880,"uid":17404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"G-drive 今年出左隻單HDD usb3.1 但行gen1 將之前 usb3.0 隻 HDD 由 7200 改做 5400 轉，賣貴左只係為左個type c 頭。<br />\n<br />\n睇唔出乜嘢理由唔買番舊usb3.0 個version<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.g-technology.com/products/g-drive-usb-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.g-technology.com%2Fproducts%2Fg-drive-usb-c&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79adtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4dbbc2b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.g-technology.com/products/g-drive-usb-c</a>"},{"pid":"e65cbab9fba096917826835ae2ef13c1128e751f","tid":371880,"uid":68446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>G-drive 今年出左隻單HDD usb3.1 但行gen1 將之前 usb3.0 隻 HDD 由 7200 改做 5400 轉，賣貴左只係為左個type c 頭。<br />\n<br />\n睇唔出乜嘢理由唔買番舊usb3.0 個version<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.g-technology.com/products/g-drive-usb-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.g-technology.com%2Fproducts%2Fg-drive-usb-c&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79adtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4dbbc2b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.g-technology.com/products/g-drive-usb-c</a></blockquote><br />\nWD嗰隻My Book Duo都好似係，轉款用USB-C頭不過仲係3.1 gen 1，根本同3.0同速，碟就照用NAS Red 5400rpm，係個盒多左兩個USB-A 3.0頭當hub用，咁全線就set高100美金，on9"},{"pid":"c949d9c4dae07d2cfb254d84c9ba2a0b0ea30e00","tid":371880,"uid":17404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"其實睇中一隻叫Akitio嘅台灣牌子，個look好襯imac. 如果行tb3 可以 諗下quad mini - support 4 x 2.5&quot;hdd or ssd <br />\n<br />\n行raid0 應該爽到冇朋友。<br />\n<br />\n但香港好似唔多人用，怕冇乜支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.akitio.com.tw/portable-storage/akitio-thunder3-quad-mini\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.akitio.com.tw%2Fportable-storage%2Fakitio-thunder3-quad-mini&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79adtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=db7518e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.akitio.com.tw/portable-storage/akitio-thunder3-quad-mini</a>"},{"pid":"e2b239a80e5ddc1086ba1ba164f246c88d10591b","tid":371880,"uid":68446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實睇中一隻叫Akitio嘅台灣牌子，個look好襯imac. 如果行tb3 可以 諗下quad mini - support 4 x 2.5&quot;hdd or ssd <br />\n<br />\n行raid0 應該爽到冇朋友。<br />\n<br />\n但香港好似唔多人用，怕冇乜支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.akitio.com.tw/portable-storage/akitio-thunder3-quad-mini\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.akitio.com.tw%2Fportable-storage%2Fakitio-thunder3-quad-mini&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79adtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=db7518e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.akitio.com.tw/portable-storage/akitio-thunder3-quad-mini</a></blockquote><br />\nSSD over TB3唔知有無TRIM，不過Akitio既4 bay enclosure應該無hardware RAID controller，要用番macOS既soft RAID咁應該有TRIM，但係soft RAID問題會去左整唔到RAID5<br />\n<br />\nbtw，Thunder3系列頭兩隻(Quad，Duo)係唔support Mac，因為佢仲早過MBP2016出，Apple唔知咩原因唔俾佢地用嗰粒TB chipset pass，呢個問題可以響Mac度裝TB Enabler解決不過部部都要裝會幾煩<br />\n<br />\n呢排出既Quad Mini，Quad X都換左新chip無左呢個問題，Quad X仲要可以插3.5&quot;<br />\n遲d有隻RAID Station係Duo既強化版，有叉電，displayport，hub，SD slot，有d似LaCie隻2big Dock"}]}